author: PRWEB
title: Symmetry Software Announces New Addition to Accounting Department
text:
It is with much pleasure, excitement and discovery to be in a mix of highly dedicated, motivated, knowledgeable people with who I am privileged to meet and work with at Symmetry Software. Scottsdale, Arizona
Symmetry Software, specialists in payroll withholding tax solutions for large employers and service providers, is pleased to announce the addition of Rita Begay to the Accounting Department. Rita will primarily be working with Symmetry’s Director of Finance Sam Kerch, serving in the capacity of accounting support.
Rita says, “It is with much pleasure, excitement and discovery to be in a mix of highly dedicated, motivated, knowledgeable people with who I am privileged to meet and work with at Symmetry Software.” Rita comes to Symmetry Software after working as an Accounting Contractor within the accounting industry for the last five and a half years. She worked with small and large corporations during that time, and gained invaluable knowledge due to the variety of projects she took part in.
Rita resides in the Phoenix, Arizona area, where she enjoys living due to the close proximity to the mountains, beach, Las Vegas, and Tucson. She also appreciates the multi-generational and cultural activities the Phoenix area has to offer.
About Symmetry Software
Symmetry Software simplifies the payroll process with accurate and dependable payroll withholding tax solutions. From Payroll Point®, the local tax identifier, and Symmetry Payroll Forms™, electronic withholding forms, to the Symmetry Tax Engine® and PaycheckCity® Calculators, Symmetry Software’s products give you the right taxes, the first time®.
